tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE income_expenses ( 
  id INT PRIMARY KEY, 
  transaction_date DATE NOT NULL, 
  description VARCHAR(255), 
  amount NUMERIC(10, 2) NOT NULL, 
  category VARCHAR(50) 
);

CREATE TABLE Expenses (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    amount DECIMAL,
    date DATE,
    category TEXT,
    description TEXT
);

CREATE TABLE FinancialReports (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    report_date DATE,
    income_total DECIMAL,
    expenses_total DECIMAL,
    net_income DECIMAL
);

CREATE TABLE Transactions (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    amount DECIMAL,
    type VARCHAR,
    source_id INT,
    destination_id INT,
    date DATE
);

CREATE TABLE Reports (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    report_date DATE,
    income_total DECIMAL,
    expenses_total DECIMAL,
    net_income DECIMAL
);
